<!-- The museum is under supervision of the Bavarian State Painting Collections which houses an expanded collection of more than 3.000 European paintings  from [[classicism|classicism]] to [[art_nouveau|art nouveau]]. About 400 paintings and 50 sculptures of these are exhibited in the New Pinakothek. -->
